  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC077">
        <l>aintā kuvatē,</l>
	<l>iṉṉeṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi</l>
	<l>yitaṉi ṉiṟṟitu veṉṉu matuvē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/209/mode/1up">209</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/210/mode/1up">210</ref>.</p>
<p/>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n250/mode/1up">247</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n252/mode/1up">249</ref>.</p>
<p>i-ḷ. mēl iṉṉeṉap peyar koṭuttōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol aintāvatām. aḵtu ipporuḷiṉittaṉmaittu ipporuḷeṉṉum poruṇmaiyai uṇarttum. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>aintāvatu nāṉkuporuṇmaiyuṭaittu; poruvum, ellaiyum, nīkkamum, ētuvumeṉa. avaṟṟuṭporuviruvakaippaṭum; uṟaḻporuvum, uvamapporuvumeṉa. ētuvumiruvakaippaṭum; ñāpakavētuvum, kārakavētuvumeṉa. avaṟṟuṇ ñāpakavētupporuṇmai mēlē kūṟappaṭṭatu. kārakavētupporuṇmai accamākkameṉpaṉavaṟṟāṟ peṟappaṭum. nīkkapporuṇmai tīrtal paṟṟuviṭutaleṉpaṉavaṟṟāṟpeṟappaṭum. ēṉaiyiraṇṭum itaṉiṉiṟṟituveṉpataṉāṟ koḷḷappaṭum, avviraṇṭaṉaiyum aḵtirumuṟaiyāṉuṇarttumākalāṉ. ellaipporuḷ - </p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC077-Cēṉ-cit1">
    karuvūriṉkiḻakku</lg><p>;</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC077-Cēṉ-cit2">
    itaṉiṉūṅku
  </lg> 
  <p>eṉa varum. kiḻakku ūṅkeṉpaṉa, viṉaikkuṟip pallavēṉum iṟṟeṉṉum poruḷpaṭa niṟṟaliṉ, iṟṟeṉṟalēyām. porūupporuṭkutāraṇam muṉṉarppeṟappaṭum.	(16)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
